OL,3,C'With rifle I kill one, with a
OL,4,Cjoystick I can kill 100': Ukraine's
OL,5,Crobot war
OL,7,FA video released by Ukraine's
OL,8,Fpresident Volodymyr Zelenskyy appears
OL,9,Fto show a Russian surrender with no
OL,10,FUkrainian soldiers in sight.
OL,12,FWhat makes it remarkable is that the
OL,13,Fenemy position was taken exclusively
OL,14,Fby unmanned ground vehicles and drones.
OL,16,FThe remotely controlled victory is
OL,17,Fbelieved to be the first of its kind
OL,18,Fin the world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
