PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778193332
OL,3,C'With rifle I kill one, with a
OL,4,Cjoystick I can kill 100': Ukraine's
OL,5,Crobot war
OL,7,FThe machines behind the operation were
OL,8,Fbuilt in Ukrainian factories that,
OL,9,Fbefore the war, produced entirely
OL,10,Fdifferent products.
OL,12,FOne company, Ratal Robotics, used to
OL,13,Fmanufacture street lights. Now its
OL,14,Ffocus is on killing machines.
OL,16,FOne of the company's military advisers
OL,17,Fshowed us around the factory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
