PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778193332
OL,3,C'With rifle I kill one, with a
OL,4,Cjoystick I can kill 100': Ukraine's
OL,5,Crobot war
OL,7,F"In the wheels, they have anti-tank
OL,8,Fmines," he said casually, before
OL,9,Fpointing out an unmanned off-road
OL,10,Fvehicle fitted with a mounted machine
OL,11,Fgun.
OL,13,F"In the past, in 2022, we go to war
OL,14,Fwith rifle and grenade. Now we go to
OL,15,Fwar with joystick and robots. War is
OL,16,Ftotally changed. With rifle I can kill
OL,17,Fone, two, maybe three of our enemies
OL,18,Fwith joystick I can kill 100."
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@GO]uD@AOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
