OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778193332
OL,3,C'With rifle I kill one, with a
OL,4,Cjoystick I can kill 100': Ukraine's
OL,5,Crobot war
OL,7,FIts vehicles are part of a rapidly
OL,8,Fevolving generation of robotic systems
OL,9,Fdesigned for combat, logistics and
OL,10,Frescue operations.
OL,12,FA UGV (unmanned ground vehicle)
OL,13,Finstructor who calls himself 'Panda'
OL,14,Fgave us a demonstration.
OL,16,F"It is really easy to train like small
OL,17,Fboys small toys. Big boys, big toys."
OL,26,@xD@AOUyD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
