OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778193332
OL,3,C'With rifle I kill one, with a
OL,4,Cjoystick I can kill 100': Ukraine's
OL,5,Crobot war
OL,7,FThe machines, which cost roughly the
OL,8,Fsame as a basic truck, can transport
OL,9,Fweapons, supplies or people. They can
OL,10,Falso be controlled from anywhere with
OL,11,Fan internet connection.
OL,13,FOne recent mission involved rescuing a
OL,14,F77-year-old woman stranded in Russian-
OL,15,Foccupied territory. The crew remotely
OL,16,Finstructed her to take a seat in the
OL,17,Fvehicle before carrying her to safety.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
