PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778193332
OL,3,C'With rifle I kill one, with a
OL,4,Cjoystick I can kill 100': Ukraine's
OL,5,Crobot war
OL,7,F"Now we are adapting and using new
OL,8,Ftechnologies because we are forced to,
OL,9,Fwe have a huge opponent with lots of
OL,10,Fresource and money supply, and we need
OL,11,Fto survive this war," Panda told us.
OL,13,FAccording to Ukrainian officials,
OL,14,Fdrones and robotic systems have
OL,15,Fcarried out more than 22,000 missions
OL,16,Fover the past three months alone.
OL,18,FBut Ukraine is not the only country
OL,19,Frapidly developing unmanned and
OL,20,Fautonomous military technology.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
