OL,3,C'With rifle I kill one, with a
OL,4,Cjoystick I can kill 100': Ukraine's
OL,5,Crobot war
OL,7,FChina has recently demonstrated
OL,8,Frobotic dogs equipped with machine
OL,9,Fguns, while companies in the UK are
OL,10,Falso expanding their capabilities.
OL,12,FAt Malloy Aeronautics, engineers are
OL,13,Fdeveloping heavy-lift drones capable
OL,14,Fof carrying up to 68 kilograms. The
OL,15,Faircraft are already being used for
OL,16,Fship-to-ship logistics and could
OL,17,Feventually serve as low-cost missile
OL,18,Fplatforms or emergency rescue vehicles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
