CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778193332
OL,3,C'With rifle I kill one, with a
OL,4,Cjoystick I can kill 100': Ukraine's
OL,5,Crobot war
OL,7,FAccording to Malloy Aeronautics CEO
OL,8,FNeil Appleton, all militaries want to
OL,9,Freduce risks to humans.
OL,11,F"Anywhere you can replace people doing
OL,12,Fdull dirty or dangerous jobs with
OL,13,Frobotics whether it's uncrewed ground
OL,14,Fvehicles or underwater vehicles or
OL,15,Fflying vehicles like ours there will
OL,16,Fbe a natural inclination to do that to
OL,17,Freduce risk to life," he told ITV News.
OL,26,@sD@AOUyD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
