PN,30709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778193332
OL,3,C'With rifle I kill one, with a
OL,4,Cjoystick I can kill 100': Ukraine's
OL,5,Crobot war
OL,7,FFor now, human operators remain part
OL,8,Fof the system. According to Malloy
OL,9,FAeronautics' chief technical officer,
OL,10,Fin the future, machines could move
OL,11,Ffrom simply following programmes to
OL,12,Feffectively 'thinking' for themselves.
OL,14,F"In the next 5 or 10 years the machine
OL,15,Fis going to be providing most of the
OL,16,Fthinking and just critical
OL,17,Fintervention from the remote pilots
OL,18,Fand the users," he said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUzD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
