CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778193332
OL,3,C'With rifle I kill one, with a
OL,4,Cjoystick I can kill 100': Ukraine's
OL,5,Crobot war
OL,7,FThe pace of development is already
OL,8,Foutstripping legislation and
OL,9,Fregulation. There are ethical
OL,10,Fquestions too.
OL,12,FBack in Ukraine, engineers say they
OL,13,Fare already working on the eighth
OL,14,Fgeneration of robotic systems
OL,15,Fdeveloped in just two years. 'Panda's'
OL,16,Fmessage to Western allies is stark:
OL,17,Finnovate or die.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
